ike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:14:14.000Z","msg":"港獨老人收皮啦"},{"pid":"7406859a5d05ff8677612d4e4207a7822ebd8949","tid":830153,"uid":50984,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:21:32.000Z","msg":"//個位本身係劉小麗佢去選返我認為無問題，但馮檢基都未參選你班泛民就無所不用其極想嚇走人唔想佢去選，仲唔係人渣？//<br />\n<br />\n人地唔係話支持基哥同小麗老麗爭呀,而係點解假設小麗老母被DQ就會自動派李卓人代佢選呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支持修改議規則嘅李卓人同廢老基有咩分別呀,睇埋內文先屌人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39d5d063954b053a9cd40cb95d10186cea30ae5","tid":830153,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:23:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3576a033a9f25de4b42c1247251e054692467e10","tid":830153,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"佢自己話過唔再選以加反口唔屌等幾時"},{"pid":"3d95f1ad09cbdd791486bef5deb0f28baba67cc0","tid":830153,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:26:36.000Z","msg":"哥基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3066c2c13880f6f7512c43a9b39a09f208353622","tid":830153,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:26:49.000Z","msg":"兩條廢老互奶<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6576292cdafb75d11a136e828e75760376f482","tid":830153,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1b36db04f10d08e462183f5931cbaca483f4b99d","tid":830153,"uid":187729,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:55:40.000Z","msg":"廢老幫翻廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:28:03.000Z","msg":"因為黃毓民選輸比劉小麗<br />\n<br />\n因此, 本身佢地有私怨<br />\n<br />\n所以黃毓民會去奶投共廢老馮檢基<br />\n<br />\n兩條都係人間垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8506b9306f6a0e66d2ee24394f4197d571e417","tid":830153,"uid":51532,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:30:39.000Z","msg":"以前都幾崇拜毓民，呢家？叫佢食能屎啦！"},{"pid":"81ed4399abc7282204fe998481cd324cdbc4776f","tid":830153,"uid":45376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:40:28.000Z","msg":"以前成日提住嘅政治倫理呢？"},{"pid":"313d0b29379ef07193be9e5b7f9083a5bf04b015","tid":830153,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0abba9d37298990b566494a28d85b3444f6514af","tid":830153,"uid":15647,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f188d11f92741baf84c5f23c90cd7411acadbf87","tid":830153,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"教主你返屋企含撚啦，當日條死廢老唔係踩過界，人哥神早入咗去鬼得閑同你爭補選咩；呢d叫自作孽不可活，當日攬炒就預咗要還啦仆街仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"明明人哥係比雷動雷走左，又關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"條廢老死去新西選咩呀"},{"pid":"0f705d4ad9c014fa30f97003fd0f5b9d188a0a23","tid":830153,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"食屎啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"48dcbfd8d57eecdaec710e2cdec7c59a75babeae","tid":830153,"uid":15647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"313d0b29379ef07193be9e5b7f9083a5bf04b015","tid":830153,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0abba9d37298990b566494a28d85b3444f6514af","tid":830153,"uid":15647,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f188d11f92741baf84c5f23c90cd7411acadbf87","tid":830153,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"教主你返屋企含撚啦，當日條死廢老唔係踩過界，人哥